OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FMost seeing
OL,6,Fclear spells overnight with
OL,7,Fintermittent areas of cloud. Winds
OL,8,Fdropping out and staying mild
OL,9,Fovernight, but more comfortable than
OL,10,Frecent nights. Light and variable
OL,11,Fwinds.
OL,12,
